  <brief_title>Pilot 99mTechnetium-MIBI Single Photon Emission Computed Tomography - Computed Tomography (SPECT-CT) in Papillary Carcinoma (CA) Thyroid</brief_title>
  <official_title>99mTechnetium-MIBI SPECT-CT for Pre-operative Evaluation of Cervical Lymph Node Metastasis in Papillary Thyroid Carcinoma; A Pilot Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
