  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to see if the 99mTechnetium-MIBI SPECT-CT can be a tool for
      preoperative evaluation of cervical node metastasis in papillary thyroid cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
